window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The bond that is forged in an ice skating rink and made stronger over many tea and coffee breaks at work eventually turns crazy when love sneaks in. </p> <p>Meera, a carefree and successful fashion blogger, falls in love with her khadoos best friend, Ishaan. Walking together, falling together, getting up together - somewhere they find their destination, only to realise that the journey itself was far better. </p> <p><i>I Think I Am in Love</i> is a story of finding friendship, chasing love, nurturing dreams and striking a balance between all of them. A story of true love trying to find a way, narrated straight from the heart.</p>"; 
